# M4 LangGraph Agent + 跨轮记忆

## 里程碑

**M4** — 用 LangGraph StateGraph 替代 M2 for 循环，MemorySaver + `thread_id` 实现跨轮对话记忆。

## 关联 Skill

| Skill | 用途 |
|-------|------|
| [add-api-endpoint](../Skills/add-api-endpoint/SKILL.md) | `thread_id` 透传 |
| [http-integration-test](../Skills/http-integration-test/SKILL.md) | 跨轮记忆集成测试 |
| [local-dev](../Skills/local-dev/SKILL.md) | 本地启动与验收 |
| [extract-ai-knowledge](../Skills/extract-ai-knowledge/SKILL.md) | `docs/knowledge/langgraph.md` |

## 范围

### 交付文件

| 文件 | 说明 |
|------|------|
| `requirements.txt` | `langgraph>=0.2.0` |
| `agent/graph.py` | StateGraph + ToolNode + MemorySaver |
| `agent/agent.py` | invoke 走图；删除 for 循环 / function_calling |
| `server/model/request/agent.py` | `thread_id` |
| `server/model/response/agent.py` | `thread_id` |
| `server/api/agent.py` | 透传 thread_id |
| `web/src/api/agent.ts` | thread_id |
| `web/src/components/ChatPage.tsx` | 保存/回传 thread_id |
